						               													<description>Hero Detected! is a board game for 2 to 4 players who are enjoying dungeon building.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player is the boss of the dungeon fantasy world, slaying, decorating your own dungeon. Curious adventurers and righteous warrior must prove their skills in the Underworld.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The idea comes from &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;the PC game Dragon Nest building from Japan. The concept art was advocating the classic RPG games, we have tried to configure the traditional fantasy world with interesting cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game you try to build the biggest dungeon to lure the most heroes in.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The players will play cards to build the dungeon and can play special action cards to mess with the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Basic Overview&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Plunder &amp;#10;Select a Village Card and place it face down. &amp;#10;If you loot the cards the card information stays private. If the card placed in the dungeon entrance it comes to a battle of the player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Purchase &amp;#10;Place a Monster over the loot card or magic card to buy this card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Building &amp;#10;Acquired by purchase monster card facilities to be placed one card per turn, and in disposing the dungeon, and be able to place all three cards, disposed on existing cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battle &amp;#10;Occurs if you have played a card at the entrance of the dungeon. By default, the proceeds from the fight card was placed on the left, and if this level is higher mowing the mighty warrior of the level as the level of the card goes to the next one. The opposite can be sent to prison veterans card. If you mighty men broke through in all the fields of the dungeon to the damage the card. Three damage card is the defeat of one player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
